Package: tartarus
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, tar (>= 1.16) | afio
Recommends: perl, curl
Suggests: gnupg, bzip2 | gzip (>= 1.3) | pbzip2 (>= 1.0.3-1) | xz-utils, lvm2, util-linux (>=2.13)
Description: script based backup system
 Tartarus is a script based backup system that relies on default
 utilities available on most regular Linux systems. It supports
 on-the-fly upload to an FTP server, compression, encryption and
 can easily be extended by hooks.
